answers.body_markdown:
See [M2E-WTP FAQ](https://wiki.eclipse.org/M2E-WTP_FAQ#How_do_I_change_the_context_root_of_my_project.3F).
It says that specifying 
```xml
&lt;properties&gt;
   &lt;m2eclipse.wtp.contextRoot&gt;/app&lt;/m2eclipse.wtp.contextRoot&gt;
   ...
 &lt;/properties&gt;
```
would do the trick. At least it does for me on Eclispe 2018-12 (4.10.0) and M2E 1.10.0

Older solutions like [this](https://www.mkyong.com/eclipse/eclipse-how-to-change-web-project-context-root/) does not seem to work.

